ou care about them, makes you cheer for them, makes you love them. you cant read this and not feel beartown and its citizens make their way into your heart. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003ei am of the strong opinion that fredrik backmans work will considered and taught as classic literature in the years to come. \u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cb\u003e↠ \u003ci\u003e5 stars\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/b\u003e","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/10171516?shelf=read"},"taggings":[{"__typename":"Tagging","tag":{"__typename":"Tag","name":"favourites","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/10171516?shelf=favourites"}}],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2411357194"},"likeCount":364,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":25,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.WRjMe3rUQikxm_TXvreHvA":{"id":"kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.WRjMe3rUQikxm_TXvreHvA","__typename":"Book"},"User:16254355":{"id":16254355,"__typename":"User","legacyId":16254355,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1464987365i/16254355._UX200_CR0,18,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":false,"textReviewsCount":1196,"viewableName":"Matthew","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/16254355-matthew","contributor":null,"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":8233},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.vbBJFgb6mTpXcKPHdnDnMw":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.vbBJFgb6mTpXcKPHdnDnMw","__typename":"Review","book":{"__ref":"Book:kca://book/amzn1.gr.book.v1.WRjMe3rUQikxm_TXvreHvA"},"creator":{"__ref":"User:16254355"},"recommendFor":"Everyone!","updatedAt":1643888848840,"createdAt":1515007360000,"spoilerStatus":false,"lastRevisionAt":1536156540000,"text":"Backman crawled in my chest and found each heartstring.\u003cbr\u003e\u003